cast.overview: The film tells a story of a divorced couple trying to raise their young son. The story follows the boy for twelve years, from first grade at age 6 through 12th grade at age 17-18, and examines his relationship with his parents as he grows.
cast.title: Boyhood

details.biography: Sean Tracey was born in California on July 18,1970. He began his music career in elementary school, playing the trumpet throughout his academic career. When he moved to Juneau, AK, he taught himself to play the guitar and harmonica. He played with the "Panhandle Crabgrass Revival Band" in Juneau for many years and won an award which enabled him to put out his own CD "Sean Tracey/Trouble". Sean plays with "The Austin Steamers" in Austin, TX (July 2014). The band has traveled over much of the Texas area and played several gigs in Alaska.  - IMDb Mini Biography
details.name: Sean Tracey
